---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Best 8-Letter Bingos in Scrabble — MAXIMIZE, QUIZZIFY, FOXHOUND"
  description="Top 8-letter Scrabble bingos with 50-point bonus. MAXIMIZE (28+50), QUIZZIFY (40+50), FOXHOUND (22+50). Strategy for landing 8-letter plays."
  keywords="8 letter bingos scrabble, maximize scrabble, quizzify scrabble, foxhound scrabble, best bingo words, 50 point bonus scrabble, eight letter words"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Best 8-Letter Bingos in Scrabble — MAXIMIZE, QUIZZIFY, FOXHOUND",
    "description": "Top 8-letter Scrabble bingos with 50-point bonus. Strategy for landing high-scoring plays.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-30",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-best-8-letter-bingos" }
  })} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How do you play an 8-letter bingo in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "An 8-letter bingo uses all 7 rack tiles plus one already on the board. You connect through an existing letter to form a valid 8-letter word, earning the 50-point bonus." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the highest-scoring 8-letter bingo?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "QUIZZIFY scores 40 base points plus 50 bonus for 90 total. MAXIMIZE scores 28+50=78. These require rare tiles but deliver game-changing scores." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Are 8-letter bingos harder than 7-letter bingos?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes — they require connecting through an existing board letter. However, they open more possibilities since you effectively work with 8 letters instead of 7." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Bingos</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Best 8-Letter Bingos in Scrabble — MAXIMIZE, QUIZZIFY, FOXHOUND</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Eight-letter bingos are the ultimate Scrabble power play. You use all 7 rack tiles plus one letter already on the board, earning the 50-point bonus while often landing on premium squares. Here are the highest-scoring 8-letter plays.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">90 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">QUIZZIFY (40+50)</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">78 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">MAXIMIZE (28+50)</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">72 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">FOXHOUND (22+50)</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">8</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letters used</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top 8-Letter Bingos Ranked</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Monster Play</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">QUIZZIFY — 90 Total Points</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">Q=10, U=1, I=1, Z=10, Z=10, I=1, F=4, Y=4 · 40 base + 50 bonus</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Two Z tiles plus Q and F make this the ultimate 8-letter bingo. Requires both Z's and Q on rack simultaneously — rare but unforgettable.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">📈 MAXIMIZE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">78 pts total · M=3, A=1, X=8, I=1, M=3, I=1, Z=10, E=1</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🦊 FOXHOUND</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">72 pts total · F=4, O=1, X=8, H=4, O=1, U=1, N=1, D=2</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⚡ OXAZEPAM</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">78 pts total · X=8, Z=10 power tiles · Drug name</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🧊 FREEZING</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">71 pts total · F=4, Z=10 · Common word</p></div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">8-Letter Bingo Strategy</h2>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Scan the board for hooks:</span> Look for single letters that extend into 8-letter words. An existing E lets you play MAXIMIZE through it. An O enables FOXHOUND.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Know your stems:</span> Common 7-letter stems like SATIRE+N, RETAIN+S can become 8-letter words through board letters. Memorise which stems extend to 8.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Position for premium squares:</span> 8-letter words span more board space, increasing odds of hitting DWS or TWS. Plan placement before committing tiles.</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">OPTIMIZE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">71pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ANALYZED</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">69pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">VAPORIZE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">72pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">EQUALIZE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">76pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Pro Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">8-letter bingos through existing letters are <span class="text-white font-medium">30% more common</span> than people think. Every board letter is a potential hook — train yourself to see 7-tile extensions through each one.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-best-7-letter-bingos/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Best 7-Letter Bingos in Scrabble</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/bingo-stem-strategy/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Bingo Stem Strategy Guide</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-cyan-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find 8-letter bingos from your tiles — free solver, instant results</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center"><a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a></div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
